    <item>
      <title>葛兰素史克股价暴跌，因制药商必须面对特拉华州的 Zantac 诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/gsk-plunges-as-drugmaker-must-face-zantac-cases-in-delaware</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法院判决英国制药商葛兰素史克公司以及赛诺菲等其他制药商必须接受有关其胃灼热治疗药物 Zantac 是否会导致癌症的审判，随后葛兰素史克公司股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/gsk-plunges-as-drugmaker-must-face-zantac-cases-in-delaware</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 07:14:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
